{"tid":2050127,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"科大阻學生重漆「青蛙路」抗爭標語","createTime":"2020-06-04T02:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T02:48:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b924a0de4a0f6fe691bf4a786d80dc94ad722b6d","tid":2050127,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200604/FQHFAKMRDXJBLPG4KDAZY3FIV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200604%2FFQHFAKMRDXJBLPG4KDAZY3FIV4%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY7KDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=5eb8b080\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200604%2FFQHFAKMRDXJBLPG4KDAZY3FIV4%2F&h=43629f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200604/FQHFAKMRDXJBLPG4KDAZY3FIV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n科大阻學生重漆「青蛙路」抗爭標語<br />\n<br />\n校方以鐵欄圍封小徑，阻止學生為抗爭標語補油。&lt;br /&gt;朱永倫攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】科技大學學生會原定昨午為賽馬會大堂小徑「青蛙路」上的「希望在於人民，改變始於抗爭」字句補油，以示延續抗爭之火。惟校方今年一改過往，不但用鐵欄圍封小徑，更用白布蓋上大字，並派出保安員駐守，拒絕讓學生補油。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：荔枝角收押所內外悼六四<br />\n<br />\n鐵欄圍封 恫嚇懲違紀學生<br />\n<br />\n科大學生會會長麥嘉俊指抗爭運動即將一周年，希望透過補油明志。麥指曾與校方多次溝通，對方以阻塞道路為由拒絕補油，麥斥說法無稽，「補番油都係一兩鐘乾曬，𠵱家由朝封到晚，到底邊個先係block traffic」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者刁欽明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JSHPRBQXSE2TYJFVLF6BVYWGLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJSHPRBQXSE2TYJFVLF6BVYWGLE.jpg&h=4692a761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科大生在校內掛起橫額，抗議校方打壓學生自由。<br />\n<br />\n去年曾參與補油的麥指，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，會集中火力為香港抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n科大回覆指，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，大學會採取紀律行動。<br />\n<br />\n■記者刁欽明"},{"pid":"730456fdcccc92dbbf510e71963ad9047fd72b3f","tid":2050127,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EUQMMUR63SPSC4GBEJOYLCCMCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEUQMMUR63SPSC4GBEJOYLCCMCI.jpg&h=351a6066&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf31bfbeff88986418ac4a6e3e463f81b7fa6930","tid":2050127,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:43:54.000Z","msg":"屎餵"},{"pid":"8c158aaa07f01f6d00a1f97e0196579d6789ee5e","tid":2050127,"uid":112486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:45:48.000Z","msg":"麥嘉俊唔係hku架咩"},{"pid":"d06e2ab5619594f3c8e0923a4de01ffa2513d611","tid":2050127,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"push"}]}